328
00:20:29,330 --> 00:20:31,120
There's(有的) protomolecule down there.

329
00:20:32,380 --> 00:20:35,080
Yeah, so it would appear.

330
00:20:35,630 --> 00:20:37,170
Apparently(显然) we are experts(专家) in the field,

331
00:20:37,170 --> 00:20:39,870
