341
00:21:05,990 --> 00:21:07,580
Oh, shit. Delay's getting(得到) bad.

342
00:21:07,580 --> 00:21:08,570
Shit.

343
00:21:09,200 --> 00:21:10,700
Take care of yourself, flyboy.

344
00:21:11,670 --> 00:21:12,910
You too, Bobbie.

345
00:21:26,560 --> 00:21:28,060
UN freighter Amberjack,

346
00:21:28,060 --> 00:21:29,470
