347
00:21:29,480 --> 00:21:31,680
Give us cargo. We no fight and you live.

348
00:21:31,690 --> 00:21:32,800
Answer now.

349
00:21:38,980 --> 00:21:42,690
Unidentified(a.) pirata, this is O.P.A.S. Tynan.

