00:21:43,200 --> 00:21:44,770
We have target lock.

351
00:21:44,990 --> 00:21:47,530
Shut down your drive. Prepare to be boarded.

352
00:21:49,660 --> 00:21:52,610
Comply, or we will be forced(被迫) to fire.

353
00:21:53,710 --> 00:21:55,240
You rabbiting, bossmang.

354
00:21:55,830 --> 00:21:57,790
Fo(男名男子名) da(爸爸) shasa.

355
