357
00:22:58,900 --> 00:23:00,060
Evasive(规避) action!

358
00:23:00,070 --> 00:23:01,470
They're dumping(倾倒) core!

359
00:23:44,280 --> 00:23:46,190
What faction(派别) are you with?

360
00:23:46,740 --> 00:23:47,980
It pay well?

361
00:23:49,450 --> 00:23:50,820
Fo(男名男子名) kill your own...

362
00:23:52,410 --> 00:23:53,780
fo da(爸爸) Inners?

363
00:23:54,410 --> 00:23:56,910
Three UN supply ships(船舶) got hit on this trade route

364
00:23:56,910 --> 00:23:58,110
