365
00:23:58,500 --> 00:24:00,830
Who is ignoring(忽视) the truce?

366
00:24:01,440 --> 00:24:03,520
The one that still fight for the Belt.

367
00:24:05,230 --> 00:24:08,190
Guess you the Inners' good little koyo now.

368
00:24:08,970 --> 00:24:10,870
Content for the table scraps.

369
00:24:12,890 --> 00:24:14,860
They keep Belters out of the Ring

370
00:24:15,340 --> 00:24:17,470
