372
00:24:20,400 --> 00:24:22,320
And you help them.

373
00:24:31,290 --> 00:24:35,550
Good little koyo.

374
00:24:48,460 --> 00:24:51,230
Rocinante, you are entering(进入) the Ring Blockade(封锁) Zone.

375
00:24:51,230 --> 00:24:53,500
Please transmit(传送) your access code.

376
00:24:53,710 --> 00:24:54,880
Roger that.

377
00:24:56,890 --> 00:24:58,260
There you go, partner.

378
00:24:59,210 --> 00:25:00,790
Code received(接收) and verified.

379
00:25:00,790 --> 00:25:02,360
You're clear for transit.

380
00:25:14,430 --> 00:25:15,570
It's nice to know Martians(火星人)

381
00:25:15,570 --> 00:25:17,410
have to go through this as well.

382
00:25:19,090 --> 00:25:21,890
Yeah, but they get to train for years(年) in one G.(G.)

383
00:25:23,300 --> 00:25:25,710
- How am I doing? - Good.

384
00:25:26,040 --> 00:25:29,420
Bone density, muscle mass, heart-lung(心肺) capacity all up.

385
