391
00:25:38,480 --> 00:25:40,360
We all lost family on Ganymede(木卫三)

392
00:25:40,360 --> 00:25:42,070
because of the Inners' war.

393
00:25:42,070 --> 00:25:44,290
- Yeah. - Ilus is(现在) our home now,

394
00:25:44,290 --> 00:25:46,770
and we will not be driven(驱动) out again.

395
00:25:46,780 --> 00:25:47,820
Yeah.

396
00:25:48,560 --> 00:25:49,690
Keep going.

397
00:26:26,980 --> 00:26:28,600
Oye, Nagata.

398
00:26:28,680 --> 00:26:30,250
What are you doing here?

399
00:26:30,620 --> 00:26:33,280
Is the universe about to end again?

400
00:26:33,360 --> 00:26:34,730
Did you think I'd miss a chance

401
00:26:34,730 --> 00:26:36,400
