402
00:26:36,900 --> 00:26:38,550
Good to see you, kopeng.

403
00:26:38,550 --> 00:26:40,900
A bit of a surprise to be seen.

404
00:26:41,250 --> 00:26:44,670
The Inners don't shoot us to pieces(碎片) with their railguns.

405
00:26:44,670 --> 00:26:46,530
We don't nuke(核武器) the Ring.

406
00:26:46,530 --> 00:26:48,630
One big happy family now, I guess.

407
00:26:48,630 --> 00:26:50,060
You've been(一直) busy, eh?

408
00:26:50,140 --> 00:26:53,170
Over 40(40) Ring comm(通信) relays(继电器) installed(安装) to date, I gather.

409
00:26:53,170 --> 00:26:57,900
