410
00:26:57,900 --> 00:27:00,590
With Medina(麦地那) Station the hub(中心) of it all.

411
00:27:01,230 --> 00:27:02,990
It's a good command.

412
00:27:02,990 --> 00:27:05,600
Only gas station on the new frontier.

413
00:27:06,080 --> 00:27:08,380
We're putting(推杆) in a souvenir(纪念品) shop.

414
00:27:08,750 --> 00:27:11,730
Be a lot of business after the blockade(封锁) lifts.

415
00:27:12,660 --> 00:27:16,220
- How is your back? - Only hurts(伤害) when I move.

416
00:27:16,480 --> 00:27:19,100
Which means nerves(神经) are regrowing, so that's(没错) good.

417
00:27:21,810 --> 00:27:23,410
You're bound for Ilus.

418
00:27:24,080 --> 00:27:24,790
That's(没错) right.

419
00:27:24,790 --> 00:27:27,180
With James Holden(霍尔顿) on the gunship.

420
00:27:28,090 --> 00:27:30,250
You're going to get the Belters off that planet.

421
00:27:30,300 --> 00:27:32,690
We're not going to evict(驱逐) anyone.

422
00:27:32,890 --> 00:27:34,340
We're going to make sure it's safe.

423
00:27:34,340 --> 00:27:35,510
Safe?

424
00:27:35,510 --> 00:27:37,380
You hear how many of those refugees(难民)

425
00:27:37,380 --> 00:27:39,440
died(死亡) trying(尝试) to adapt?

426
00:27:39,620 --> 00:27:42,270
A lot of them had to go back up to orbit.

427
00:27:42,980 --> 00:27:46,100
They were foolish(愚蠢) to think they could live there.

428
00:27:46,250 --> 00:27:48,710
It's not foolish(愚蠢) to want free air

429
00:27:48,710 --> 00:27:51,650
and free water and a home for their children.

430
00:27:52,400 --> 00:27:54,400
We are creatures(生物) of space.

431
00:27:54,500 --> 00:27:58,030
In two generations, their children(孩子) will be Inners.

432
00:27:58,170 --> 00:28:00,570
They won't(不会) even remember what they were.

433
00:28:00,580 --> 00:28:03,720
Everyone should have the right to decide for themselves.

434
00:28:04,050 --> 00:28:05,110
Of course.

435
00:28:11,710 --> 00:28:13,680
Xalte to sif, Camina.

436
00:28:13,680 --> 00:28:15,310
Dewe(德威) fasi, Nagata.

437
00:28:22,650 --> 00:28:24,680
We won't(不会) be able to assess how badly the Belters

438
00:28:24,680 --> 00:28:26,220
have contaminated(污染) the atmosphere(大气)

439
00:28:26,220 --> 00:28:28,120
until we've(我们已经) actually been(一直) on the planet,

440
00:28:28,120 --> 00:28:30,350
but once you're there, I'm hoping(希望) we can

441
00:28:30,350 --> 00:28:33,080
convince them of the need to limit the damage.

442
00:28:33,080 --> 00:28:34,990
I'm looking(看) forward to working with you, Captain.

443
00:28:35,190 --> 00:28:36,740
We'll see you on New Terra.

444
00:29:36,970 --> 00:29:38,340
We're through the Ring.

445
00:29:39,350 --> 00:29:41,660
Be on Ilus in a few weeks. Then what?(什么？)

446
00:29:42,060 --> 00:29:43,310
I'll(我会) let you know.

447
00:29:44,110 --> 00:29:45,250
Thanks for the ride.

448
00:29:45,620 --> 00:29:47,800
What...what are we supposed... Wait!

449
00:30:08,580 --> 00:30:10,780
Got something you want to say to me, sailor?

450
00:30:13,610 --> 00:30:14,480
Can I...

451
00:30:18,810 --> 00:30:20,050
Can I buy you another beer?

452
00:30:23,840 --> 00:30:25,700
