454
00:30:28,040 --> 00:30:29,450
You're all civilians(平民) now."

455
00:30:30,160 --> 00:30:31,880
Had a promotion(推广) coming(来了) up too.

456
00:30:31,880 --> 00:30:33,810
That's(没错) the shit(该死) end of the stick.

457
00:30:34,260 --> 00:30:35,400
You should know.

458
00:30:36,180 --> 00:30:37,910
I watched(观察) your hearing on the feed.

459
00:30:38,890 --> 00:30:40,580
You could've saved(保存) your benefits(福利) if you signed(签字的)

460
00:30:40,580 --> 00:30:42,490
