461
00:30:42,490 --> 00:30:44,090
I'm sure it was good entertainment(娱乐).

462
00:30:44,090 --> 00:30:46,170
- But you wouldn't. - I stand by what I did,

463
00:30:46,170 --> 00:30:47,840
