464
00:30:47,840 --> 00:30:48,860
That's(没错) what a Marine does.

465
00:30:48,860 --> 00:30:50,610
First they order you to lie.

466
00:30:51,070 --> 00:30:52,870
Then they strip you of your pension,

467
00:30:53,050 --> 00:30:55,800
