468
00:30:55,800 --> 00:30:58,630
And he doesn't bitch(婊子) and whine(哀号) when the chips(薯条) are down.

469
00:30:58,630 --> 00:31:00,800
He goes to the VA, gets(得到) a regular job...

470
00:31:00,800 --> 00:31:02,900
I'm there every goddamn(该死的) day waiting(等待) in line.

471
00:31:02,900 --> 00:31:05,370
The problem is, you've(你有) got too much time to think.

472
00:31:05,370 --> 00:31:06,340
It's making(制造) you crazy.

