477
00:31:12,590 --> 00:31:14,740
You're not exactly the poster(海报) girl for mental health.

478
00:31:14,740 --> 00:31:16,230
I didn't vent(发泄) yours.

479
00:31:16,230 --> 00:31:18,120
Oh, bleeding(流血) heart.

