527
00:34:21,050 --> 00:34:22,090
Maybe you will.

528
00:34:22,090 --> 00:34:23,630
This planet has no geological(地质) activity.

529
00:34:23,630 --> 00:34:24,620
And isn't(不是) that amazing?

530
00:34:24,620 --> 00:34:25,840
