533
00:34:29,420 --> 00:34:31,510
- that we had the charter(租船合同) for. - How'd that go?

534
00:34:31,510 --> 00:34:34,250
We gave(给) them a percentage(百分比) of the take, 300K,

535
00:34:34,250 --> 00:34:36,080
