546
00:35:16,760 --> 00:35:18,430
Hold tight!

547
00:37:47,430 --> 00:37:48,530
There's(有的) one over here!

548
00:37:51,690 --> 00:37:52,890
Give me the mask!

549
00:37:55,690 --> 00:37:57,260
It's okay. Come here.

550
00:38:06,340 --> 00:38:07,930
Twenty-three(二十三) of our people are dead,

551
00:38:07,930 --> 00:38:09,310
